"{\n  \"text\": \"Hi everybody, Scotty here. I'm looking to become a market gardener. And part of my strategy is not just to sell the fresh produce, in fact, maybe not sell very much of that at all, but try to make value added products out of my knowledge of food preservation to sell them at value added. So when I grow eggplant, which grows really well here in Houston, Texas, I won't sell that as eggplant, which no one really knows what to do with. I'll make Baba Ganoush out of it. I'll smoke that stuff and get my little kitchen staff uh going with that and give them some extra hours from and value add that. When I grow cucumbers, I'll make pickles out of that. I can sell a jar of pickles for a lot of money, but selling a big bag of cucumbers, which is the same effort for me, not very much. So I'm gonna try to do a lot of value-added food preservation stuff, and then I'll have my garden extend for three to six months with all that food and have it metered out in a way I can sell it better. And you know, that's gonna be my strategy. Anyway, thanks, y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hi everybody, Scotty here.\",\n      \"start\": 0.88,\n      \"end\": 2.72,\n      \"duration\": 1.84,\n      \"confidence\": 0.99,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" Hi\",\n          \"start\": 0.88,\n          \"end\": 1.2,\n          \"duration\": 0.32,\n          \"confidence\": 0.976\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 1.28,\n          \"end\": 1.36,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 0.999\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"yb\",\n          \"start\": 1.36,\n          \"end\": 1.52,\n          \"duration\": 0.16,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"ody\",\n          \"start\": 1.52,\n          \"end\": 1.6,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 1.0\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \",\",\n       